# V2T-CoT: From Vision to Text Chain-of-Thought for Medical Reasoning and Diagnosis
## A demo dataset for R-Med 39K

We constructed R-Med 39K (Medical Instruction-tuning dataset) with reasoning paths from four Med-VQA datasets for Text CoT, integrating them into VLM training for reliable rationale validated by both LLMs and experts.


## Detailed Code and complete datasets will be publicly available soon.
